### API for get comments by post id
GET localhost:8080/api/v1/comments/post/1

### API for create comments with post id
POST localhost:8080/api/v1/comments/post/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Cảm ơn bạn đã chia sẽ",
  "postId": 1,
  "userId": 2
